{"tid":458539,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"陳偉豪：真正落實主客制","createTime":"2017-11-05T03:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T03:45:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"088d06d39bd8551d5ea26ad49a63d0bd5dfd4d96","tid":458539,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/130948/thumbnail/d2228c25e1e7764a5c4cec3ccdcc62ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F130948%2Fthumbnail%2Fd2228c25e1e7764a5c4cec3ccdcc62ff.jpg&h=de8db865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過多番爭議，R&amp;F富力的主場廣州燕子崗體育場終於開放，繼2004年澎馬流浪隊北上東莞作客南城地產並發生球員衝突後，首次有香港聯賽於內地舉行。<br />\n<br />\nR&amp;F富力對夢想FC賽前一天，兩軍球員於主場出席賽前記者會，更是港超首次有「官方」規格舉辦聯賽。夢想隊長陳偉豪坦言，今次安排真正實踐了港超的主客制。<br />\n<br />\n香港01記者蘇子暘　廣州直擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955398/xlarge/7d04705d16a67064fa6d80cac4740080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955398%2Fxlarge%2F7d04705d16a67064fa6d80cac4740080.jpg&h=3d3c7730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港超聯：富力雖然邀請傳媒北上採訪，出發前曾指可拍攝一小時訓練，但最後馬里科（中）不願公開全課，只開放了頭15分鐘訓練。（蘇子暘攝）<br />\n<br />\n廣州燕子崗體育場設施及周圍環境<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955433/xlarge/5bd4d6ad0a45452efb868879d96de873.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955433%2Fxlarge%2F5bd4d6ad0a45452efb868879d96de873.jpg&h=dc543e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955431/xlarge/54c55da42646dc9855471689c467d358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955431%2Fxlarge%2F54c55da42646dc9855471689c467d358.jpg&h=7a548d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955435/xlarge/ed8ff41c630de1ccdb747f2b97b5f0a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955435%2Fxlarge%2Fed8ff41c630de1ccdb747f2b97b5f0a8.jpg&h=b0e5c750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955432/xlarge/2b1e58142ce3383c5902ae5c395bf170.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955432%2Fxlarge%2F2b1e58142ce3383c5902ae5c395bf170.jpg&h=9ecb2a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955434/xlarge/09c997fb6d4053a64701540f21c15141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955434%2Fxlarge%2F09c997fb6d4053a64701540f21c15141.jpg&h=e79dfa55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955437/xlarge/4c2db72abd592ca1654f38e346288358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955437%2Fxlarge%2F4c2db72abd592ca1654f38e346288358.jpg&h=ee10dc0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955436/xlarge/81681da437194bd7acea11056c1c49dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955436%2Fxlarge%2F81681da437194bd7acea11056c1c49dd.jpg&h=3773f8b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由香港過關往深圳灣，再乘包車兩小時方到燕子崗體育場。球場四周是民居，比賽球場有大廈，附近亦有足球場讓公眾踢波，十分平民化；目測看台的觀眾席重新安裝，可容納約1000名球迷。沒有隨隊、自行到球場的夢想後衛梁國威說，作客燕子崗總算沒有想像中不便。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955401/xlarge/51711369972e6acb7b05bb2d3e5d39f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955401%2Fxlarge%2F51711369972e6acb7b05bb2d3e5d39f3.jpg&h=1ad2594a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港超聯：富力中場伊達指球隊平時的訓練基地離球場只得20分鐘車程，十分方便。（蘇子暘攝）<br />\n<br />\n首先出席記者會的是富力教練馬里科，他指球隊目前有不少傷停球員，被問到球隊今季於各項賽事只得1勝3負，他解釋：「頭兩場我們踢得很好，只是犯了點錯誤致敗，過去訓練我嘗試幫助球隊減低失誤。要數的話，近幾場表現我都滿意，上場贏波更不用說了。」對於富力首次於「主場」迎戰港超球隊，馬里科直言是個好消息：「可以在廣州主場比賽已是進步，不論在燕子崗還是別處，希望明年可在更好的球場吧。」富力操練時，工作人員還在球場安裝設施，後衛曾健晃更指全隊首次來燕子崗練波，但草地較「跌」，有點像斧山道球場，似乎主場還有改善空間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955412/xlarge/6cff64f840f53b5db43ba0bb87602c78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955412%2Fxlarge%2F6cff64f840f53b5db43ba0bb87602c78.jpg&h=3052f7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港超聯：羅拔圖大讚富力所有安排都十分完善，又指其懷孕妻子明日將會來看比賽，十分期待。（蘇子暘攝）<br />\n<br />\n馬里科亦談及今次為港超史上首次舉辦賽前記者會：「我在之前的訪問說過，無論是主場或作客，有記者會是最好的，因為這可讓大家討論比賽的問題、交流意見，如果沒有這種平台去討論，便少了個機會去進步。」陳偉豪亦同意此舉對年輕球員是個新體驗：「港超聯成立了數季，今年真正感受到主客制，我們要搭幾小時車上來，又要住一晚，真的感受作客環境有分別，準備要更充足，以休息為例，比賽前一天我們會放鬆，之後便回家，對年輕球員來說都是個體驗和進步的機會。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955415/xlarge/766efbdaed17414e5d76e02eac4b0860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955415%2Fxlarge%2F766efbdaed17414e5d76e02eac4b0860.jpg&h=e7eba5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港超聯：梁志榮指富力安排球隊入住的酒店，與以前他效力南華時所住過的相同，感覺特別。（蘇子暘攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955428/xlarge/25c816efc883241870be251d4afe28fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955428%2Fxlarge%2F25c816efc883241870be251d4afe28fc.jpg&h=42cd74d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港超聯：陳偉豪於記者會表現輕鬆，又笑對記者說特意上來一定要問問題。（蘇子暘攝）<br />\n<br />\n去季任R&amp;F助教兼領隊的夢想FC主帥梁志榮，亦認同有官方式的記者會是件好事，今仗倒戈亦分析富力的實力：「基本上富力和去季是兩支不同的球隊，首先有外援，3名本地球員又是入籍球員，實力上已經很不同，但我相信他們的默契和板斧不及我們，主要靠速度、個人技術及長波，沒有什麼特別。」馬里科早前曾指，港式足球踢法很簡單，細榮特意回應：「我不明白他說的港式足球是什麼意思，我們踢地波的，不是每隊都是這樣（大腳斬），是你暫時見到的球隊會這樣踢。」"},{"pid":"66b9c8b2ec2cd7606d65a819a2647fdf7f6f6d0c","tid":458539,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955429/xlarge/7abe63da77d48a1d557b805873cd28c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955429%2Fxlarge%2F7abe63da77d48a1d557b805873cd28c2.jpg&h=47a9f8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港超聯：入選大港腳初選名單的鄭展龍（中）於操練時輕舒腳頭。（蘇子暘攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955448/xlarge/fe619cf02bd42c9a9e4ddc9ef29cf431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955448%2Fxlarge%2Ffe619cf02bd42c9a9e4ddc9ef29cf431.jpg&h=a9ae9fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955447/xlarge/4deed31ed388e6e42dfeae6b2f250998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955447%2Fxlarge%2F4deed31ed388e6e42dfeae6b2f250998.jpg&h=9ab4665a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955452/xlarge/1b90c78dea76f43610b753a8108cc108.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955452%2Fxlarge%2F1b90c78dea76f43610b753a8108cc108.jpg&h=d71c385a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955449/xlarge/440bc7c81441e262478c987fb64804e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955449%2Fxlarge%2F440bc7c81441e262478c987fb64804e8.jpg&h=41c2d0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/955451/xlarge/a14301c99b880a2be608656eb660a186.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F955451%2Fxlarge%2Fa14301c99b880a2be608656eb660a186.jpg&h=0ae14e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撰文：蘇子暘<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/130948/-%E6%B8%AF%E8%B6%85%E8%81%AF-%E5%AF%8C%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%BB%E5%A0%B4%E9%AC%A5%E5%A4%A2%E6%83%B3FC%E9%A6%96%E8%BE%A6%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83-%E9%99%B3%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA-%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A6%E4%B8%BB%E5%AE%A2%E5%88%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F130948%2F-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%2581%25AF-%25E5%25AF%258C%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A2%25E6%2583%25B3FC%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25B1%25AA-%25E7%259C%259F%2